{"type": "article", "id": 20978, "title": "水泥和木材的储物盒", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-20T07:40:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122314wGFb7uYmrgjzs2pI.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是土耳其设计师 Derya Arpaç 的储物盒系列，由两个水泥圆筒和 4 块木质圆片组成。木片充当了底座和盖子，却也可以拿出来单独使用，它可以是储物盒，也可以是展示珠宝的容器。两种自然材料之间有天然的反差，有实验性，也能恢复成传统的使用方式。设计师试图以此打破了人们对日常用品的惯例用法，<a href=\"http://deryaarpac.com/Intentionally-Non-Intentional\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072615070543dKMIRV8BXafWjZ.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"450\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.55012225\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150705oeKrNR85LW4sAPcO.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"450\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.55012225\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150705encT8x7MWaoNGYg0.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"450\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.55012225\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150706So8YXWHrRqglcsn0.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"450\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.55012225\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}